<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.7.8">
<l>veṟiyār karuṅkūnta lāycciyar vaitta</l>
<l>vuṟiyār naṟuveṇṇey tāṉukan tuṇṭa</l>
<l>ciṟiyāṉai ceṅka ṇeṭiyāṉaic cintit</l>
<l>taṟiyātā reṉṟu maṟiyātār kaṇṭāmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who do not comprehend thinking of the bright-eyed, tall one,</l>
<l>The little one who ate relishing the fragrant butter</l>
<l>Which filled the pot nets kept by the herdess with dark fragrance-filled curls,</l>
<l>Never comprehend [anything]; [this] we have seen.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
